name: Sun Flower #1
description:
Sun Flower is the first issue of the wanatana series (#1). Sunflower tells the story of a woman who loves to paint, it can be seen from the hat she wears. This woman also wore a sweater by wanatana with a sunflower design made with hand embroidery techniques.
.
As an appreciation for the collection of wanatana's works in the first series, wanatana will give a physical gift.
.
